    # Mv "I knew you were up to no good. What were you talking about? What are you planning here, some kind of attack?"
    Mv "네 놈이 뭔가를 꾸미고 있다는 건 진작에 눈치챘지. 무슨 얘기를 한거지? 뭘 계획하고 있는거야? 공격?"

# game/chapter1.rpy:2874
